Text: FMR LLC grew its stake in shares of Travelers Companies by 9.4% in the first quarter. FMR LLC now owns 10,500,482 shares of the insurance provider's stock worth $1,440,247,000 after acquiring an additional 904,028 shares during the last quarter.
